title: No. 9 Tech routs Baylor, 11-1 - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 9 Tech routs Baylor, 11-1 - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: WACO, Texas – No. 9 Texas Tech cruised to an 11-1 victory against Baylor on Saturday afternoon at Baylor Ballpark. The win clinched the series, and Tech's fifth Big 12 series win in six tries this season.
